# Phase 3 Rules — Core Diagnostics

## What This Phase Builds

- Metric registry and benchmark registry (124 KPIs from the Basic Analytic Data Set)
- 7 domain diagnostic packages: vacancy/turnover, make-ready/maintenance, leasing/CRM, listing quality, pricing/revenue, competitive position, property condition
- Scoring engine implementing the 12-area, 65-item, 315-sub-item scoring structure
- Contradiction engine detecting PM-vs-field and cross-source mismatches
- Impact engine with 10 reusable financial impact models
- Evidence-backed finding compiler producing the finding graph

## Prerequisites

Phase 2 must be complete: `fact_unit_day` materialized, vacancy and make-ready cycles built, all ClickHouse fact tables populated, unit-day spine queryable for every unit for every day in scope.

